---
---

<section id="docs">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Useful Docs</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Go Deeper</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Guides and references for getting the most out of Coherence.
      </p>

      <div class="docs-grid">

        <a href="/getting-started" class="doc-card">
          <div class="doc-icon">&#9654;</div>
          <div class="doc-content">
            <h3>Getting Started</h3>
            <p>Step-by-step setup guide &mdash; from install to your first guardrails.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/scope" class="doc-card">
          <div class="doc-icon">&#9673;</div>
          <div class="doc-content">
            <h3>Scope & Lifecycle</h3>
            <p>How user, project, and session scopes interact across repos and terminals.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/plugins" class="doc-card">
          <div class="doc-icon">&#9881;</div>
          <div class="doc-content">
            <h3>Plugin Reference</h3>
            <p>All 10 plugin skills &mdash; commands, arguments, and output formats.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/reference" class="doc-card">
          <div class="doc-icon">&#9776;</div>
          <div class="doc-content">
            <h3>File Map & Uninstall</h3>
            <p>Every file Coherence touches, organized by scope, plus removal steps.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .docs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .doc-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-mid);
    border: 1px solid var(--bg-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .doc-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 255, 240, 0.3);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
  }

  .doc-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 2.25rem;
    height: 2.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 240, 0.2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(0, 255, 240, 0.05);
  }

  .doc-content h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .doc-content p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .docs-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
